'''熊奕韬'''（{{lang-en|Jeffery Xiong}}，{{bd|2000年|10月30日}}），美国华裔[[国际象棋|国际象棋]]棋手、[[国际象棋特级大师|国际象棋特级大师]]。

熊奕韬祖籍中国[[湖南|湖南]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/go/2016-07-26/doc-ifxuhukv7459849.shtml|title=美籍华裔少年参加中国国象联赛 父亲:全力支持|date=2016-07-26|work=新浪竞技|access-date=2016-11-17|archive-date=2016-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127154348/http://sports.sina.com.cn/go/2016-07-26/doc-ifxuhukv7459849.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，出生于美国[[得克萨斯州|得克萨斯州]][[普莱诺_(得克萨斯州)|普莱诺]]。他于2010年被授予棋联大师称号。<ref name=fide>{{fide|id=2047640}}</ref>2012年，获世界国际象棋12岁组亚军。2014年， 晋升为国际大师。<ref>[http://www.fide.com/component/content/article/1-fide-news/7043-list-of-titles-approved-by-the-2nd-quarter-presidential-board-2013.html List of titles approved by the 2nd quarter Presidential Board 2013] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fide.com/component/content/article/1-fide-news/7043-list-of-titles-approved-by-the-2nd-quarter-presidential-board-2013.html |date=20160920091603 }}. FIDE.</ref><ref name=fide/>2015年获美国青年锦标赛亚军，并于同年晋升为[[国际象棋特级大师|特级大师]]。2016年3月，其[[等级分|等级分]]首次超过2600分。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ratings.fide.com/top_files.phtml?id=2047640|title=Top List Records|publisher=FIDE|access-date=2016-11-17|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122165723/https://ratings.fide.com/top_files.phtml?id=2047640|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年，他又先后夺得了卡帕布兰卡纪念赛B组冠军<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://en.chessbase.com/post/looking-back-xiong-in-the-capablanca|last=Ramirez|first=Alejandro|title=Looking back: Xiong in the Capablanca|date=2016-07-03|website=Chess News|publisher=ChessBase|access-date=2016-11-09|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121054714/https://en.chessbase.com/post/looking-back-xiong-in-the-capablanca|dead-url=no}}</ref>、美国青年锦标赛冠军<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://en.chessbase.com/post/jeffery-xiong-wins-u-s-junior|2=|last=Ramirez|first=Alejandro|title=Jeffery Xiong wins U.S. Junior|date=2016-07-19|website=Chess News|publisher=ChessBase|access-date=2016-11-09|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121033300/https://en.chessbase.com/post/jeffery-xiong-wins-u-s-junior|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[世界青年国际象棋锦标赛|世界青年锦标赛]]冠军。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chessdom.com/jeffery-xiong-and-dinara-saduakassova-are-2016-world-junior-champions/|title=Jeffery Xiong and Dinara Saduakassova are 2016 World Junior Champions|date=2016-08-21|publisher=Chessdom|access-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228053013/http://www.chessdom.com/jeffery-xiong-and-dinara-saduakassova-are-2016-world-junior-champions/|archive-date=2016-12-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

